# =============================================================================
# Spark Match Knowledge Base (00-knowledge-base) - .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Generado segun ADR-003 branch-based deployment y adaptacion a vault Obsidian.
# Version: 1.1.0 - 2026-07-09
# Tipo: Solo docs (Markdown, decisiones, SDD) + config compartida de Obsidian
# Referencia: .admin/obsidian-viability-analysis.md
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# IDEs
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Obsidian: estado personal (NO compartir entre usuarios)
# Cada usuario tiene su propio layout de workspace y config de graph.
# Estos archivos son regenerados por Obsidian automaticamente.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/graph.json
.obsidian/cache/
.obsidian/plugins/
.obsidian/themes/Personal/
.obsidian/hotkeys.json

# --- Excepciones: la config compartida SI debe commitearse ---
!.obsidian/app.json
!.obsidian/appearance.json
!.obsidian/core-plugins.json
!.obsidian/community-plugins.json

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Obsidian: trash y caches
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.trash/
.cache/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Documentacion autogenerada
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
docs/api/
docs/build/
*.pdf.local

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Imagenes y adjuntos pesados (referenciar con wikilinks, no trackear los binarios)
# Si necesitas versionar imagenes, ponerlas en attachments/ y agregar nombre
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# attachments/*  # (comentado: descomentar si el vault se vuelve pesado)

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local drafts (no compartir)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
drafts/
private/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Notas personales locales
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
TODO_local.md
NOTAS_PERSONALES.md
.scratch/
